# mode0_demo exercise: scroll the 64-wide field, flip the sprite, scroll back.
# Frame numbers assume the bundled BIOS (~60-frame bootstrap; cart ready ~f62).
70   screenshot bin/mode0_boot.png
80   press      RIGHT
200  release    RIGHT
210  screenshot bin/mode0_scrolled.png
220  tap        A
240  screenshot bin/mode0_flipped.png
260  press      LEFT
340  release    LEFT
350  screenshot bin/mode0_back.png
